          'The key metrics that VE impacts include Total Cost of Ownership (TCO), Return on Investment (ROI), risk reduction (measured in breach probability, compliance gaps, or exposure windows), productivity gains (hours saved per analyst, tickets deflected), and employee experience scores. Each of these can be quantified and tied back to financial outcomes that resonate with decision-makers.',
